lieid="61" src="https://www.discuss.com.hk/images/smilies/default2/funk.gif"/&gt;&lt;img alt="" border="0" smilieid="61" src="https://www.discuss.com.hk/images/smilies/default2/funk.gif"/&gt;&lt;img alt="" border="0" smilieid="61" src="https://www.discuss.com.hk/images/smilies/default2/funk.gif"/&gt;&lt;img alt="" border="0" smilieid="61" src="https://www.discuss.com.hk/images/smilies/default2/funk.gif"/&gt;&lt;img alt="" border="0" smilieid="61" src="https://www.discuss.com.hk/images/smilies/default2/funk.gif"/&gt;&lt;img alt="" border="0" smilieid="61" src="https://www.discuss.com.hk/images/smilies/default2/funk.gif"/&gt;&lt;img alt="" border="0" smilieid="61" src="https://www.discuss.com.hk/images/smilies/default2/funk.gif"/&gt;&lt;/img&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=31940976&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=1113890913683790702c8a82_85374412"/><published>2025-05-28T23:45:38+08:00</published></entry><entry><id>ad98286a0b817e69ebb4c3c8b30dbe3f</id><title>今年上28000</title><updated>2025-05-29T00:03:24+08:00</updated><author><name>omegahk</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-05-29T00:03:24+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_572607010"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_572607010"&gt;牛市永遠都喺懷疑失信心中誕生同成長&lt;br&gt;我覺得而家港股同美股都係牛市階段&lt;br/&gt;個個以為已經貼緊高位陸續沽貨&lt;br/&gt;誰不知好消息一嚟，就會一窩蜂湧入股市&lt;br/&gt;直上28,000 （牛二）&lt;br/&gt;其實而家每日嘅成交量有2000億左右已構成牛市一期必相配嘅成交量&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;好消息就係而家美國息率隨時升&lt;br/&gt;只要特朗普一出關稅威脅，佢啲新國債就冇人買，息率就升 。而息率一升，佢就無計可施，急急腳縮沙又延長談判期等等…&lt;br/&gt;聯儲局亦都非常關注國債息率，可以隨時減息&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;所以特朗普威脅關稅嘅手段已經唔多&lt;br/&gt;相反迫下迫下，佢只好陸續促成同歐洲同埋中國嘅貿易協議，以表政績！&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;只要無手段再用關稅威脅，一切就會向好！&lt;br/&gt;再冇大壞消息，牛二！&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=31940986&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=1113890913683790702c8a82_85374412"/><published>2025-05-29T00:03:24+08:00</published></entry><entry><id>c1403e0d22a8ca48d4103367814110c6</id><title>鈍刀子割肉</title><updated>2025-05-29T06:00:28+08:00</updated><author><name>setyoufree</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-05-29T06:00:28+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_572608385"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_572608385"&gt;陰跌 牛又增加 有排跌 大戶是鈍刀子割肉 温水煮青蛙&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=31941061&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=1113890913683790702c8a82_85374412"/><published>2025-05-29T06:00:28+08:00</published></entry><entry><id>b93ca5eeea6f6b0036b92b2a18c2368d</id><title>聽聞度度都裁員, 是否好難搵工?</title><updated>2025-05-17T22:37:18+08:00</updated><author><name>不移動</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-05-17T22:37:18+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_572449070"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_572449070"&gt;如題&lt;img alt="" border="0" smilieid="61" src="https://www.discuss.com.hk/images/smilies/default2/funk.gif"/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=31930411&amp;utm_source=festival_fid&amp;utm_medium=57&amp;utm_campaign=1057&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC"/><published>2025-05-17T22:37:18+08:00</published></entry></feed>